import React from 'react';
import { Box, Typography, Grid, Paper } from '@mui/material';
import BuildIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Build';
import DesignServicesIcon from '@mui/icons-material/DesignServices';
import CodeIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Code';
import SupportAgentIcon from '@mui/icons-material/SupportAgent';

const Services = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ maxWidth: 1200, mx: 'auto', mt: 6, px: 0 }}>
      <Typography variant="h4" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom align="center" sx={{ px: 2 }}>
        Hizmetler
      </Typography>
      <Typography
        variant="body1"
        align="center"
        color="text.secondary"
        mb={6}
        maxWidth={700}
        mx="auto"
        sx={{ px: 2 }}
      >
        Profesyonel olarak verdiğim hizmetlere aşağıdan ulaşabilirsiniz
      </Typography>
      <Grid container spacing={3} sx={{ px: '20px' }}>
        {/* 1. Kutu */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={6} lg={3} sx={{ display: 'flex' }}>
          <Paper
            elevation={0}
            sx={{
              border: '2px solid #90caf9',
              bgcolor: 'transparent',
              p: 3,
              textAlign: 'left',
              borderRadius: 3,
              width: '100%',
              display: 'flex',
              alignItems: 'center',
              gap: 2,
              minHeight: 120,
              transition: 'transform 0.3s ease',
              '&:hover': {
                transform: 'scale(1.05)',
                borderColor: '#64b5f6',
                boxShadow: '0 0 10px #90caf9',
              },
              // Burada istediğin pozisyon stillerini verebilirsin
              // Örnek: marginTop: '10px', veya position: 'relative', left: '5px'
            }}
          >
            <BuildIcon sx={{ fontSize: 50, color: '#90caf9' }} />
            <Box>
              <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>
                Web Geliştirme
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Modern ve duyarlı web uygulamaları geliştiriyorum.
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* 2. Kutu */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={6} lg={3} sx={{ display: 'flex' }}>
          <Paper
            elevation={0}
            sx={{
              border: '2px solid #90caf9',
              bgcolor: 'transparent',
              p: 3,
              textAlign: 'left',
              borderRadius: 3,
              width: '100%',
              display: 'flex',
              alignItems: 'center',
              gap: 2,
              minHeight: 120,
              transition: 'transform 0.3s ease',
              '&:hover': {
                transform: 'scale(1.05)',
                borderColor: '#64b5f6',
                boxShadow: '0 0 10px #90caf9',
              },
            }}
          >
            <DesignServicesIcon sx={{ fontSize: 50, color: '#90caf9' }} />
            <Box>
              <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>
                UI/UX Tasarım
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Kullanıcı dostu ve şık tasarımlar oluşturuyorum.
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* 3. Kutu */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={6} lg={3} sx={{ display: 'flex' }}>
          <Paper
            elevation={0}
            sx={{
              border: '2px solid #90caf9',
              bgcolor: 'transparent',
              p: 3,
              textAlign: 'left',
              borderRadius: 3,
              width: '100%',
              display: 'flex',
              alignItems: 'center',
              gap: 2,
              minHeight: 120,
              transition: 'transform 0.3s ease',
              '&:hover': {
                transform: 'scale(1.05)',
                borderColor: '#64b5f6',
                boxShadow: '0 0 10px #90caf9',
              },
            }}
          >
            <CodeIcon sx={{ fontSize: 50, color: '#90caf9' }} />
            <Box>
              <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>
                Yazılım Danışmanlığı
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Proje ihtiyaçlarınıza özel çözümler sunuyorum.
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* 4. Kutu */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={6} lg={4} sx={{ display: 'flex' }}>
          <Paper
            elevation={0}
            sx={{
              border: '2px solid #90caf9',
              bgcolor: 'transparent',
              p: 3,
              textAlign: 'left',
              borderRadius: 3,
              width: '100%',
              display: 'flex',
              alignItems: 'center',
              gap: 2,
              minHeight: 120,
              transition: 'transform 0.3s ease',
              '&:hover': {
                transform: 'scale(1.05)',
                borderColor: '#64b5f6',
                boxShadow: '0 0 10px #90caf9',
              },
            }}
          >
            <SupportAgentIcon sx={{ fontSize: 50, color: '#90caf9' }} />
            <Box>
              <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>
                Teknik Destek
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Sorunlarınızı hızlı ve etkili şekilde çözüyorum.
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Services;
